		" That the page is not already in use
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" That the name will not be used for something more important in future (such as the name of a game or an article about a topic)
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" That the page name is derived from the user's name in a sane way
		$LF
	]li
	[li 
		" That it is a valid 
		(__wikiLink|TextFormattingRules|wiki name)
		". In particular, remember that capital letters start a new word in title of the page, and that special characters such as -,+/*?\'<>(){}[]&" and space are 
		[em 
			"not
		]em
		" allowed.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
